Resources: Things in your domain.
In case of a course API topics are the resouces.
Once we have identified then we can look into the way the consumers can access the resources using different HTTP Methodds.

GET     /topics       Get all topics
GET     /topic/id     Gets the topic
POST    /topics       Create new toic
PUT     /topics/id    Updates the topic
DELETE  /topics/id    Deletes the topic
